rows.label: tev000595_MSG0001
rows.name:
Evening, [ST:playername ].
Funny running into you here, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0002
rows.name:
I was just about to go have dinner with Mathias and
Lieutenant Irina.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0003
rows.name:
But the lieutenant wanted to buy something at that
store, so I'm just waiting for her to finish.
Shouldn't be too long now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_JNK0010
rows.name: Support

rows.label: tev000595_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest that Gwin buy a present for Irina.

rows.label: tev000595_JNK0020
rows.name: Propose

rows.label: tev000595_SEL0021
rows.name: Offer to take Irina's place at dinner.

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0004
rows.name: A...present? What?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0005
rows.name:
Um, so, yeah. Today isn't any sort of special day,
and I don't have any reason to give her one, sooo...
Yeah. I think she would find that pretty suspicious.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0006
rows.name:
But I HAVE been thinking that I might use my share of
our next assignment reward to get her something really
incredible for her birthday.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0007
rows.name:
Like maybe that new assault rifle from Sakuraba
Industries? What do you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0008
rows.name:
Are you insane? Irina would be FURIOUS!
Hell, the only thing I'd be eating for dinner would be
the burst grenade she'd shove down my throat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0009
rows.name:
And after all the time I spent planning to get her
something really great for her birthday, she probably
wouldn't even accept it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0010
rows.name:
I already put a preorder down on that new Sakuraba
Industries assault rifle, but...yeah. I still don't know if
that's the best gift for her or not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_JNK0030
rows.name: Suggest Meredith & Co.

rows.label: tev000595_SEL0031
rows.name: Recommend a Meredith & Co. weapon instead.

rows.label: tev000595_JNK0040
rows.name: Suggest Candid & Credible

rows.label: tev000595_SEL0041
rows.name: Recommend Candid & Credible protective wear instead.

rows.label: tev000595_JNK0050
rows.name: Suggest a Ring

rows.label: tev000595_SEL0051
rows.name: Recommend that Gwin buy Irina a ring.

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0011
rows.name: A weapon from Meredith & Co., huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0012
rows.name: Well, if that's your suggestion, I'm sure she'd love it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0013
rows.name:
Maybe I should take a closer look at some of the other
options instead of just grabbing that Sakuraba one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0014
rows.name: Thanks for your opinion. It means a lot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0015
rows.name: Oh, looks like she's coming back out now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0016
rows.name:
Well, I've got to go.
Hope we can work together on a mission soon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0017
rows.name: Protective wear from Candid & Credible?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0018
rows.name:
Well, the lieutenant really loves her weapons,
but she doesn't put much effort into her armor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0019
rows.name:
So that might actually make a better gift.
Thanks for the idea, [ST:playername ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0020
rows.name:
But wait. Isn't the ladies' wear from Candid & Credible
designed to look kinda like a...miniskirt?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0021
rows.name: Oh! Looks like the lieutenant's coming back out now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0022
rows.name: Well, uh, I better go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0023
rows.name:
Let's discuss the details of this equipment later.
...Like how in the heck I'd convince her to wear it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0024
rows.name: ...Seriously?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0025
rows.name: That's moving a bit fast, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0026
rows.name:
I mean, I don't even know if I have enough money.
I'd have to buy a matching set of rings, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0027
rows.name:
Huh... I wonder if instead of buying a pre-made one,
I could make one out of resources mined through
FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0028
rows.name:
But what resource should I use? Maybe dawnstones?
Or everfreeze ore?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0029
rows.name: Uh-oh! Looks like the lieutenant's coming back out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000595_MSG0030
rows.name:
Well, I've got to go.
Hope we can work together on a mission soon.[ST:wait ]
